@startuml
title App Use Case Diagram

left to right direction

skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #DDEEFF
skinparam ActorBorderColor #3366AA
skinparam UsecaseBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam UsecaseBorderColor #555555
skinparam ArrowColor #333333
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFFCC
skinparam NoteBorderColor #AAAAAA

actor User

rectangle "Mobile Application" {
  usecase "View Data" as UC_View
  usecase "Load Content" as UC_Load
  usecase "Retry Load" as UC_Retry
}

User --> UC_View : initiates

UC_View ..> UC_Load : <<include>>
UC_Retry ..> UC_View : <<extend>>\ncondition: load failed

note right of UC_Load
  Calls repository → Dio remote
  data source → API server.
  Returns domain model on success
  or error on failure.
end note

note right of UC_Retry
  Available when the previous
  load attempt has failed.
end note

@enduml
